(190, 'Obliteration VI', 3, 32, '9', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_1', 'With passion & purpose, we present this series of experimental hop-driven beers. Using different hop varieties & brewing techniques, we aim to educate the palate & challenge the hophead in you.Obliteration VI is a Double IPA brewed with Summit Summit and Summit Summit and Summit');
