(214, 'Tall Tale Pale Ale', 3, 26, '5', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_1', 'Big and bold, our Pale Ale distinguishes itself by its huge, fresh hop aroma and flavor. A combination of Cascade and Centennial hops, both in the kettle and during an extensive dry-hopped conditioning time, gives this beer its nectarious flavor.'),
