(382, 'Shelter Pale Ale', 3, 26, '5', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_2', 'This is our original brew and our most approachable beer. It\'s brewed with a premium barley and whole-leaf Glacial & Warrior hops. Our Shelter Pale Ale has a fine malt backbone and a slightly nutty flavor. A versatile, quaffable beer. The Shelter Pale Ale is available exclusively in the Mid-Atlantic region.'),
(383, 'Chicory Stout', 3, 42, '5', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_1', 'A dark beer made with a touch of roasted chicory, organic Mexican coffee, St. John\'s Wort, and licorice root. Brewed with whole-leaf Cascade and Fuggles hops, the grains include pale, roasted & oatmeal.'),
(384, 'Ipswich IPA', 3, 31, '6', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_0', 'Our IPA is an unfiltered cross between an English and American IPA, with a strong, dry bitterness balanced with a slight malty sweetness. A mixture of first-rate U.S. and Belgian malts, combined with English roasted barley and highly hopped with Cascade and Warrior hops make our IPA a brewery favorite.'),
(385, 'Ipswich Original Ale', 3, 26, '5', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_0', 'Named one of the World\'s Ten Best Beers by Wine Spectator Magazine, Ipswich Ale has satisfied discerning craft beer drinkers since 1991. A North Shore classic, Ipswich Ale is a medium-bodied, unfiltered English style pale ale with subtle hoppiness and a smooth malty flavor.'),
(386, 'Ipswich Oatmeal Stout', 1, 21, '7', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_2', 'Deep, rich, and malty with hints of chocolate and coffee. It\'s what espresso would be if it had the gumption to be beer. We use three different hop additions, specially selected crystal malts, roasted barley, and oatmeal to give it a soft and silky mouth feel. Makes a great dessert. Or meal.'),
(387, 'Ipswich Dark Ale', 3, 38, '6', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_1', 'Rich in color and bold in taste, our U.S. style Brown Ale combines roasted malt with two additions of specialty selected hops to produce a well-balanced ale with a satisfying finish.'),
