(391, 'Ipswich Harvest', 3, 33, '7', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_0', 'Highly regarded among hop-lovers, our Harvest Ale is a balanced and flavorful autumnal offering, to be enjoyed during the cool, crisp days of fall. We use a darker Caramunich malt and just a touch of chocolate malt along with a blend of Warrior, Ahtanum, and Columbus hops.'),
