(471, 'General Washington Tavern Porter', 2, 25, '7', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_0', 'By George, I think we\'ve got it.Days of debate and deliberation at Independence Hall were often followed by nights of debate and deliberation (and a few libations) at the City Tavern where our forefathers would gather to exchange revolutionary ideas. where our forefathers would gather to exchange revolutionary ideas.Rich and warming with a deep garnet hue the molasses-based Tavern Porterâ„¢ reflects Washington\'s admiration of Philadelphia-style porters and follows a recipe Washington used himself the molasses-based Tavern Porterâ„¢ reflects Washington\'s admiration of Philadelphia-style porters and follows a recipe Washington used himselfRich and warming with a deep garnet hue the molasses-based Tavern Porterâ„¢ reflects Washington\'s admiration of Philadelphia-style porters and follows a recipe Washington used himself when brewing beer to satisfy his thirsty field officers. when brewing beer to satisfy his thirsty field officers.Historical note: Our new brewery is located just blocks away from the site of Robert Hair\'s brewery where Washington\'s favorite Philadelphia Porter was crafted.\" where Washington\'s favorite Philadelphia Porter was crafted.\"Historical note: Our new brewery is located just blocks away from the site of Robert Hair\'s brewery where Washington\'s favorite Philadelphia Porter was crafted.\"41678,88.8'),
(472, 'Acme California Pale Ale', 3, 26, '5', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_1', 'This easy-drinking Pale Ale revives the name of one of the early icons of California brewing. Clean-tasting and pleasantly malty, Acme Pale is brewed with Yakima Valley hops, American two-row malt and British specialty malts for depth.'),
