(565, 'Schlappeseppl Export', 8, 95, '6', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_2', 'A classically brewed export beer with a slight aroma of hops.'),
(566, 'Rockslide IPA', 3, 31, '7', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_0', 'If being in one of the coldest places in the US isn\'t extreme enough, the contents of this beer may very well redefine your commitment to the pursuit of hops. Rockslide IPA is brewed in the \'West Coast\' style with aggressive amounts of American hops such as Amarillo, Centennial and Summit hops. You are greeted with a full frontal assault of citrus/grapefruit/pine hop character, followed up with malt to balance the mouthfeel. This beer is all about hops.'),
(567, 'Riverwest Stein Beer', 8, 95, '0', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_1', 'Delicious'),
(568, 'Kennebunkport IPA', 3, 31, '0', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_0', 'Below-average but drinkable IPA, cheaply priced (~$1/bottle), and available at Trader Joe\'s.'),
(569, 'Harpoon IPA', 3, 31, '6', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_1', 'From their site:\\\"\"The high hopping of Harpoon IPA is not only noticeable in the nose but especially in the finish. The lingering bitter finish of this beer is not harsh or astringent\" in part in part\\\"\"The high hopping of Harpoon IPA is not only noticeable in the nose but especially in the finish. The lingering bitter finish of this beer is not harsh or astringent\" in part by dry hopping â€“ a technique that involves adding fresh hops to the conditioning beer to provide a fresh hop aroma. by dry hopping â€“ a technique that involves adding fresh hops to the conditioning beer to provide a fresh hop aroma.The overall character is a cloudy appearance with a citrus-like aroma and clean finish.  Serve with a lemon.\\\"\" and clean finish.  Serve with a lemon.\\\"\"The overall character is a cloudy appearance with a citrus-like aroma and clean finish.  Serve with a lemon.\\\"\"'),
(570, 'Stone 11th Anniversery Ale', 3, 29, '9', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_1', 'The inspiration for making a Black IPA (or should we say \\India Black Ale/ IBA\\\"?) has been over a year in the making. As soon as we wrapped up the brewing of the Stone 10th Anniversary IPA'),
(571, 'Gumballhead', 11, 116, '5', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_1', 'Three Floyds official summer beer highly dry hopped American wheat beer. Quite hoppy. Gumballhead is brewed from red wheat and amarillo hops. It has a medium haze, due to bottle conditioning'),
(572, 'Honker\'s Ale', 1, 4, '0', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_2', 'Honkerâ€™s Ale combines a spicy hop aroma with a rich malt middle to create a perfectly balanced ale that is immensely drinkable. A smooth, drinkable English Bitter for those looking for more from their beer.'),
(573, 'Primo', 8, 95, '0', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_1', 'A rich golden liquid with a unique flavor and aroma that comes from a touch of raw Hawaiian cane sugar. Primo is a premium lager that represents the best of both worlds'),
