(594, 'Hefeweizen', 4, 50, '6', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_2', 'Paulaner Hefe-WeiÃŸbier is the best-selling beer by the Paulaner Brewery. Specially produced top-fermented yeast is what gives it its unmistakeable character: sparkling light, fruity, and just a tiny bit bitter. Because it is not filtered during the brewing process, it retains its originality and the many vitamins, minerals and trace elements.'),
