(614, 'Damnation', 5, 72, '7', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_2', 'Damnation has extraordinary aromas of banana and pear with mouth filling flavors of sweet malt and earthy hops. The lingering finish is dry and slightly bitter but very, very smooth.'),
