(652, 'Patriots Pilsner', 7, 77, '5', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_1', 'A traditional European Pilsner light in body and color. This brew possesses mild hoppy flavors and a crisp clean finish. It is made with traditional European hops: Hallertau and Saaz.'),
