(909, 'Yellow Snow IPA', 3, 31, '0', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_1', 'Yellow Snow IPA was originally introduced for the 2000 Winter Olympics in Salt Lake City.Yellow Snow is Rogueâ€™s tribute to winter sports everywhereâ€”downhill skiing snowboarding snowboardingYellow Snow is Rogueâ€™s tribute to winter sports everywhereâ€”downhill skiing snowboarding cross country cross countryYellow Snow is Rogueâ€™s tribute to winter sports everywhereâ€”downhill skiing snowboarding cross country ice hockey ice hockeyYellow Snow is Rogueâ€™s tribute to winter sports everywhereâ€”downhill skiing snowboarding cross country ice hockey ice fishing ice fishingYellow Snow is Rogueâ€™s tribute to winter sports everywhereâ€”downhill skiing snowboarding cross country ice hockey ice fishing snowmobiling snowmobilingYellow Snow is Rogueâ€™s tribute to winter sports everywhereâ€”downhill skiing snowboarding cross country ice hockey ice fishing snowmobiling and even curling.  and even curling. 4995Abita Purple HazeAbita Purple Haze4995Abita Purple Haze4.754.75'),
