(1199, 'Old Faithful Ale', 3, 26, '0', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_3', 'ur Old Faithful Ale is a Pale Golden Ale with a crisp body and light malt sweetness. We cold condition this ale to give it a pleasantly smooth character and dry palate. The Willamette and imported UK Goldings hops give this beer a light floral hop aroma, making it exceptionally easy to drink.'),
