(1253, 'Puget Brown Porter', 2, 25, '6', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_0', 'Our brown porter is brewed with eight different malts to produce a smooth, well balanced, dark beer. A specially roasted barley provides a hint of chocolate. 5.6% ABV'),
