(1255, 'B.O.R.I.S. The Crusher Oatmeal-Imperial Stout', 3, 43, '9', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_2', 'This Bodacious Oatmeal Russian Imperial Stout will crush you like no other! This is the grand-daddy of all stout styles, with an intensely deep roasted and full bodied flavor. A robust hop character adds a refreshing balance.'),
