(1265, 'Shiva IPA', 3, 31, '5', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_3', 'A generous portion of American hops create a crisp citrus nose combined with a light, sweet finish â€“ a well balanced beer that destroys the paradigm of an IPA.'),
