(1300, 'Howl', 8, 95, '5', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_3', 'Born of dark and cold and snow in the marrow of the northeast\'s longest night, HOWL comes in on wailing winds with winter-weary eyes burning holes in sunless shadows. In its darkened depths out inner voids are warmed.'),
(1301, 'Whitetail Golden Ale', 3, 37, '5', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_2', 'Our golden American ale has a crisp body and slightly dry, hoppy finish. This is a real treat for the beer lover. Pale, wheat and torrified wheat malts are used with Northern Brewer and Mt. Hood hops.'),
(1302, 'DuganA IPA', 3, 32, '9', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_3', 'Lupulin Rapture Incarnate! As fervent Â devotees of hops, we found ourselves on a quest to create a transcendental IPA capable of quenching our voracious lupulin desires. Our mantra became \\unity of bitterness'),
(1303, 'Golf', 4, 50, '5', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_1', 'A Brewer\'s Select Series, Golf is a fest-weisse hybrid or \'Festeweizen.\' It will weigh in at 5.0% and is made with Munich, Wheat, and CaraVienna malts and Spalt hops.'),
(1304, 'Old Salt IPA', 3, 31, '6', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_2', 'Our India Pale Ale is hoppy and bitter with a nice sweet malt finish. Slow dry-hop conditioning brings out the herbal hop aromas.'),
(1305, 'Cascade Razberry Wheat', 11, 121, '5', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_3', 'Razberry Wheat is crisp with a refreshing tartness and the fresh aroma of raspberries. This salmon pink ale is just the thing to transport you to berry time in the summer.'),
(1306, 'Celtic Copper Ale', 3, 33, '5', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_0', 'Celtic Copper is a mahogany hued ale with rich malt flavor and subtle hop balance'),
(1307, 'Ring Tail Pale Ale', 3, 26, '4', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_0', 'Ring Tail Pale is light in body and straw-gold in color, with a crisp hop finish. This beer is a great choice for domestic lager drinkers.'),
(1308, 'Bad Billy Blond Bock', 7, 91, '6', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_3', 'Our Blond Bock is gold in color and features a malty profile and a spicy finish courtesy of Saaz hops. This beer boasts the flavor of a traditional Bock without the cloying aftertaste.'),
(1309, 'Cascade Apricot Ale', 5, 70, '9', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_2', 'Features the intense aroma of fresh-picked, slow ripened Northwest apricots warmed by the summer sun. Based on a Belgian Tripel, this beer went through 16 months lactic fermentation and aging in French oak wine barrels.');
