(1355, 'Plead the 5th Imperial Stout', 3, 43, '12', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_0', 'It\'s big and full bodied with lots of roasted malts and balanced with heavy hops to put this imperial in a league of its own.'),
(1356, 'Unfiltered Double Simcoe IPA', 3, 32, '9', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_3', 'In 750ml corked â€™nâ€™ caged bottles this will be and unfiltered, fully bottle conditioned version of the super popular Double Simcoe. Expect Cask taste in a bottle, with more pronounced hoppy flavor and aroma due to being unfiltered. Also, carbonation will be a bit higher as is usual in our cork n cage series in keeping with tradition. It all comes together to form a uniquely great experience for hopheads.'),
(1357, 'Arctic Panzer Wolf', 3, 32, '9', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_3', 'A dry and stupendously hopped medium bodied Imperial IPA brewed with Canadian two-row malt, dextrose sugar and lots of American hops. Arctic Panzer Wolf has superior aromas of marmalade, white wine, pine and apricot all mixed with an intense American hop bitterness.'),
(1358, 'Free Loader Double Red IPA', 3, 32, '0', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_1', 'Free Loader Double Red IPA was \\double-brewed\\\". [How\'s that for a catchy term that those BiG brewers can\'t TouCH. I love it'),
(1359, 'D.O.R.I.S. the Destroyer Double Imperial Stout', 3, 43, '11', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_0', 'This extreme Double Oatmeal Russian Imperial Stout will overwhelm, satisfy, and destroy your taste buds like no other!! D.O.R.I.S. is even darker, hoppier, and stronger than our gold medal winning B.O.R.I.S. The Crusher Stout. Dry hopped and first wort hopped and first wort hopped with the finest American hops for a great Imperial hops for a great Imperial Stout experience! Enjoy the darkness!'),
(1360, 'Hop Dam Triple IPA', 3, 32, '10', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_2', 'Some say â€œbigger is better!â€. At Hoppinâ€™ Frog, we built a massive hop dam to handle the enormous amount of hops added to this colossal American Triple I.P.A. An intense experience of citrus and piney hop character is complimented by layers of rich malt flavor. Behold our new standard for hoppy beers.'),
(1361, 'Frosted Frog Christmas Ale', 11, 141, '9', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_2', 'The essence of Christmas is captured in this very bottle you are holding. Perfectly blended spices compliment Frosted Frogâ€™s rich malt flavors, creating the ultimate Christmas experience. Celebrate the holidays as you savor this very special seasonal offering.'),
(1362, 'Fresh Frog Raw Hop Imperial Pale Ale', 3, 26, '8', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_1', 'Special hoppy flavors and aromas are captured by adding freshly picked, undired hops during the harvest.These wet hops impart a character unlike other brews that is quite unique and satisfying for those who love hops â€“ the spice of beer. Smell the hop fields that is quite unique and satisfying for those who love hops â€“ the spice of beer. Smell the hop fieldsThese wet hops impart a character unlike other brews that is quite unique and satisfying for those who love hops â€“ the spice of beer. Smell the hop fields smell the freshness.\" smell the freshness.\"These wet hops impart a character unlike other brews that is quite unique and satisfying for those who love hops â€“ the spice of beer. Smell the hop fields smell the freshness.\"57828,48.4'),
(1363, 'Outta Kilter Wee-Heavy Scotch Red Ale', 1, 15, '8', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_3', 'Rich, malty flavors of caramelized and toasted grains dominate this strong Scotch ale. A hint of rye adds a crisp, Scotch-like, old-world beer character, reminiscent of a simpler life from centuries ago. â€œIt is a wee bit heavyâ€'),
(1364, 'Barrel-Aged B.O.R.I.S. Imperial Stout', 3, 43, '9', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_2', 'Made from our B.O.R.I.S. Imperial Stout, that was rated one of the Worldâ€™s 50 Best Beers, and won the Gold Medal at the GABF in 2008. BARREL-AGED B.O.R.I.S. has picked up rich characters of vanilla, dark fruit, oak, and spice. Itâ€™s unbelievably complex and savory'),
(1365, 'Hop Master\'s Abbey Belgian-style Double IPA', 5, 72, '9', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_2', 'American hops and Belgian abbey beer flavors intermingle to create a spicy and assertive beer style all their own. Citrusy character from select hops dominate this assertive Double I.P.A., complimented by a unique Belgian flavor to add complexity and ultimate beer satisfaction. The result is a flavor combination thatâ€™s a whirlwind of taste sensations.'),
(1366, 'Mean Manalishi Double I.P.A.', 3, 32, '8', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_3', 'Explore the extremes of hops, and experience all of their bitterness, flavor and aroma with this Double I.P.A. An extreme, super-assertive and satisfying amount of American hop character is balanced with a toasty, caramelized, intense malt presence.'),
(1367, 'Hoppin\' To Heaven IPA', 3, 31, '7', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_1', 'Raise your glass to the heavens in a toast to HOPS â€“ the spice of beer! This classic American I.P.A. features the finest American hops to add a spicy, assertive, and citrusy character to its full-bodied, rich malt taste'),
(1368, 'Silk Porter', 2, 25, '6', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_2', 'Dark, robust and silky-smooth, with many flavors of roasted, toasted and caramel malts. Porter is an old-world beer style, so popular that it helped start the industrial revolution. Taste the history.'),
(1369, 'Gulden Fraug Belgian Ale', 5, 65, '11', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_1', 'Smooth malt flavors of this golden Belgian-style abbey ale are complimented by traditional imported ingredients. A slightly spicy and complex flavor makes this European celebration-style beer unique and refreshing'),
(1370, 'Wild Frog Wheat', 4, 50, '6', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_3', 'Traditional German-style, unfiltered wheat beer, with a lively balanced flavor. Although no fruit or spices were used in the brewing, these flavors are created by fermentation with special yeast from the oldest brewery in the world. Try Wild Frog Wheat with a slice of orange for a crisp, refreshing experience'),
(1371, 'Smashing Berry Ale', 11, 121, '4', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_3', 'An abundance of fresh, natural fruit flavor makes this beer something special. You would think we picked the fruit moments before brewing.'),
(1372, 'Smashing Berry Dark', 11, 121, '0', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_0', 'Fresh, natural fruit flavor and a hint of chocolate malt makes this dark beer something really special. The just picked, fresh fruit flavor is very evident in this beer.'),
(1373, 'Blackout Stout', 3, 43, '9', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_3', 'A Russian Imperial Stout with a hearty malt body and bold hop flavor.'),
(1374, 'Apex', 3, 32, '8', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_3', 'Crafted with a blend of American and English malts and aggressively hopped with Pacific Northwest hops, this beer reflects what our brewers believe to be the Apex of IPA.'),
(1375, 'Paradise Porter', 2, 25, '5', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_0', 'This medium bodied porter has notes of roasted and chocolate malts, making it a perfect balance of sweet and bitter.  Generous hops give this brew a dry finish.'),
(1376, 'Iron Thistle', 1, 15, '8', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_3', 'Break out the bagpipes with your lederhosen! Weâ€™re proud to present our Iron Thistle Scotch Ale â€“ Rahrâ€™s first National Grand Champion winner. This dark, Scottish ale has a bold taste dominated by a smooth, sweet maltiness balanced with a low, hoppy bitterness. So don your kilts and enjoy. Hereâ€™s to your health â€“ SlÃ inte! Prosit!'),
(1377, 'Tres Blueberry Stout', 3, 42, '5', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_3', 'A full bodied stout made with all malted barley and blueberry. Flavors of chocolate, roast malt and light blueberry make up the palate with lots of fruity blueberry aroma.'),
(1378, 'Fore Smoked Stout', 3, 42, '0', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_3', 'Brewed with all malted barley and peat malt (smoked malt). This beer is full bodied with chocolate, roasted barley flavors, and a smokey almost BBQ finish.'),
(1379, 'One Oatmeal Stout', 1, 21, '0', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_2', 'Number one in a series of five stouts produced to help ease you through the cold and grey midwestern winters. This beer is full bodied with hints of chocolate, roasted barley, coffee flavors and a nice creamy head.'),
(1380, 'Too Cream Stout', 1, 20, '0', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_3', 'This beer is made with milk sugar (lactose) which gives this beer a nice creamy mouth feel which mingles with hints of chocolate and roasty flavors.'),
(1381, 'Three Guy Off The Scale Barley Wine', 3, 35, '15', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_3', 'A barley wine style ale brewed to 15% alc with hints of raisin, chocolate, carmel, sherry, cherry, and alcohol, just to name a few and this beer will only get better with age.'),
(1382, 'Duet', 3, 31, '7', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_2', 'A West Coast IPA. Our original single IPA made with Simcoe and Amarillo hops â€œin harmony.â€ 1.065 OG 45 IBU 7%ABV'),
(1383, 'Nelson', 3, 31, '7', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_0', 'A Golden Rye IPA.An outstanding hop from New Zealand Nelson Sauvin Nelson SauvinAn outstanding hop from New Zealand Nelson Sauvin is generously used throughout the brewing and dry-hopping of this unique beer. European rye is added for a smooth is generously used throughout the brewing and dry-hopping of this unique beer. European rye is added for a smoothAn outstanding hop from New Zealand Nelson Sauvin is generously used throughout the brewing and dry-hopping of this unique beer. European rye is added for a smooth malty addition to flavor. 1.065 OG 7%ABV\" malty addition to flavor. 1.065 OG 7%ABV\"An outstanding hop from New Zealand Nelson Sauvin is generously used throughout the brewing and dry-hopping of this unique beer. European rye is added for a smooth malty addition to flavor. 1.065 OG 7%ABV\"58066,56.5'),
(1384, 'Humidor Series Jai Alai Cedar Aged India Pale Ale', 3, 31, '8', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_0', 'he Humidor Series is a rotating offering of Cigar City Brewing beer aged on cedar. Cedar has a more subtle effect on beer than more traditional woods like oak. But, we think that once you taste it youâ€™ll agree that cedar deserves a place alongside oak in the brewerâ€™s wood-aging toolbox.'),
(1385, 'Marble India Pale Ale', 3, 31, '6', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_2', 'Congratulations! By drinking Marble Brewery India Pale Ale, you show exceptionally good taste. Our obsession with quality and attention to detail ensures that every bottle will meet your high expectations. The Columbus, Amarillo and Centennial hops lend a fragrant citrus aroma and snappy hop character. We think you will agree that this is one rock solid beer.'),
(1386, 'Mongo Double IPA', 3, 32, '9', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_0', 'A Double IPA brewed in memory of the brew cat.  In honor of Mongo, Mike Rodriguez made his first Double IPA, as he loved the cat and wanted to honor him with this beer. This 8.5% abv beer was made with Columbus hops (Mongoâ€™s Birthname), Cascade for the Mama cat, and Simocoe because that is Mikeâ€™s favorite hop.'),
(1387, 'Hopportunity Knocks Ale', 3, 31, '7', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_0', 'IPA brewed with 100% Centennial hops. Big round mouthfeel, very perfumey. Different from our canned IPA. Gotta love the Pacific NW!'),
(1388, 'Legbiter Ale', 1, 1, '5', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_0', 'Brilliant golden ale with an inviting citrus fragrance of late added Cascade and Glacier hops. The fine hop and light malt aromas carry through to the palate to give an ale that is full but refreshing, with a clean caramel malt bitter finish.'),
(1389, 'St. Patrick\'s Best', 1, 3, '4', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_3', 'Light and refreshing on the palate, our session best bitter has a classic Irish malt & traditional hop aroma.  Light amber in colour, this smooth beer has hints of caramel with a woody bitterness.'),
(1390, 'Barelegs Brew', 1, 1, '5', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_2', 'Golden with a hint of red (towards sunset). Barelegs tastes of fresh fruit, especially red current and malt fragrance. Full drinking with a subtle hoppy finish. Refreshing for a beer of this strength.'),
(1391, 'St. Patrick\'s Gold', 11, 116, '5', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_1', 'Our smooth yet powerful wheat beer is unusually refreshing on the pallet.  Golden in colour, St. Patrick\'s Gold is brewed with barley and wheat malt. Citrus peel and coriander are added to the Goldings and Saaz hops for a symphony of authentic flavour.'),
(1392, 'St Patrick\'s Ale', 1, 1, '6', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_2', 'A deep copper coloured traditional Irish Ale with highly developed and complex flavours. St Patrickâ€™s Ale/Dark is brewed with four malts and two hops, carefully married together to complement eachother producing a satisfying full flavour, ending with a Styrian late hop for a truly brilliant finish.'),
(1393, 'Manheim Red', 3, 33, '5', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_3', 'Our flagship beer, is amber to red in color with a medium body, slight caramel sweetness, and a balance more towards malt than hops. This beer is a true crowd-pleaser and keeps you coming back for more.'),
(1394, 'Bourbon County Brand Coffee Stout', 3, 43, '13', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_3', 'Everyday Goose Island smells the wonderful coffee roasting next to our brewery at Chicago\'s Intelligentsia Coffee and Tea. They put the same passion and skill into their coffee as Goose Island does with its beer. This excellent stout is made with Black Cat Espresso beans from our friends next door. You\'ll like the combination.'),
(1395, 'The Angel\'s Share - Bourbon Barrel Aged', 3, 30, '13', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_2', 'own in Kentucky and across the pond in Scotland, distillers who age their whiskeys for many years refer to the evaporation of the spirits from their barrels as \\The Angel\'s Share.\\\" We couldnâ€™t agree more. Each time a barrel is filled'),
(1396, '2x4 India Pale Ale', 3, 32, '7', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_0', '2x4 India Pale Ale (7% ABV, 65 IBUs) sports Columbus, Nugget and Amarillo hops for a spicy, citrusy blend in both flavor and aroma.  Backed by golden pale malts and a kick from flaked rye, the hops are pleasantly robust with just the right touch of bitterness at the end.'),
(1397, 'Simcoe Single Hop IPA', 3, 31, '7', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_1', 'The first in a new series of single hop IPA\'s from Mikkeller. Brewed with Simcoe, known for many great US micro-brews. An extremely fresh-hopped IPA.'),
(1398, 'Kryptonite Imperial IPA', 3, 32, '9', 'assets/img/Mockup/mockup_beer_2', 'American style double IPA, full bodied malt flavor supports a ridiculous amount of hops, giving it pronounced bitterness and overwhelming hop flavor and aroma. Made with 5 pounds of hops per barrel.');
